{"tid":961524,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入黎比下意見","createTime":"2018-12-30T07:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T15:49:53.000Z","uid":228557,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d16d30f22b9607df7637b6495c3f94568e664d03","tid":961524,"uid":228557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"有朋友同佢男朋友拍左3年拖 男方同女方都係同年大家都係20出頭 最近大家開始傾將來但傾唔掂分手了 但前提大家之前都相安無事 不過係少見左啲姐<br />\n<br />\n男方唔想結婚生BB 但女方想要 但唔係呢一刻聽佢講好似係4-5年後<br />\n<br />\n男方就話：呢一刻真係唔想要 到時都唔知想唔想要 唔想去到女方29/30歲先話唔想結唔想要 到時就真係哂左女方啲青春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就算女方之後想點樣傾諗辦法去解決 男方都唔肯改變[black]<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/black]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟價值觀唔同係咪一段感情的大忌 定係男方一早想分手只不過咁岩有呢件事可以借題發揮<br />\n<br />\n佢問左呢個問題好多次 但真係唔知男仔角度係點諗 所以各位巴絲比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f48c350e12e6854227ba5b387a26011fb0cc20","tid":961524,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd13ae3dea75814e11471096790e321b1b97ff24","tid":961524,"uid":62648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"男仔未玩夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680fabab9a2af5e574b2dd3849ba1e8cb0196365","tid":961524,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:46:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔想結婚?"},{"pid":"a54bb7aa6f82f0e4a416e92d62eb581324bb1b89","tid":961524,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f48c350e12e6854227ba5b387a26011fb0cc20","tid":961524,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T0